tourBios.exmtStatus: Conditional - Finished 142nd at 2015 Web.com Tour Qualifying Tournament
tourBios.carHigh: Won the 2010 and 2011 Provo Open, as well as the Parker Open in 2010 and 2013.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Qualified for U.S. Public Links as a sophomore at BYU...Finished the season with two top-10 finishes...Played in all 12 events his junior and senior year...Recorded three top-20 finishes his senior year and named Academic All-Conference...Named 2008 Utah Golfer of the Year.
tourBios.personal: Wife, Cara, is a beauty blogging sensation and cosmetics-line owner and creator...Together own a startup cosmetics company...Served an LDS mission to the Baltic States (Russian speaking)...Walk-up song at the first tee would be "Danger Zone" by Kenny Loggins...Majored in Russian at BYU and speaks fluent Russian...Bucket list items include watching Duke v. UNC at Cameron Indoor.
